							<p class="apple-subtitle">Follow these steps to sign up for an iOS Developer Account with Apple</p><!-- img 1 -->
							<ol class="apple-title-order">
								<li>Go to: https://developer.apple.com/enroll/</li>
								<li>Select <a href="#">Start Your Enrollment</a>
								</li>
